WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:09.450 --> 00:00:13.500
To create a New training on Virtual Reality
you need to go to Trainings -- New training

00:00:13.500 --> 00:00:15.800
and select Virtual Reality.

00:00:16.500 --> 00:00:18.400
Select the Terrain you want to create the new route from.

00:00:28.400 --> 00:00:30.100
you will get a top view of the selected Terrain.

00:00:30.200 --> 00:00:35.000
By scrolling the zoom wheel on your mouse
you will zoom in on the Terrain

00:00:35.200 --> 00:00:38.400
With a double left mouse click
you will select the starting point of the course.

00:00:45.500 --> 00:00:48.900
and double click down the route you want to
follow and create a route this way

00:01:04.100 --> 00:01:07.500
by holding one of the numbered points you can redirect the route

00:01:58.000 --> 00:02:02.100
When you have created a route, give it a name and Save it

00:02:09.500 --> 00:02:13.500
If you want to Edit an existing ride you need
to go to Trainings -- Edit training

00:02:13.600 --> 00:02:17.300
select the Terrain and then the Trainings Programs

00:02:21.700 --> 00:02:25.890
You can Edit the training by pulling the Start
or Finish down the route or by picking up

00:02:25.890 --> 00:02:28.800
the numbered points and move these so the
route is changed

00:02:34.150 --> 00:02:36.629
by editing you will lose all your score files

